longBusinessSummary: McRae Industries, Inc. manufactures and sells military combat boots for the United States Army. It also imports and sells western and work boots. The company provides its products for men, women, and children under the Dan Post, Laredo Western Boots, Dingo, McRae Industrial, and McRae Footwear brand names. McRae Industries, Inc. was founded in 1959 and is headquartered in Mount Gilead, North Carolina.
